{"tid":1343066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輿論戰刻不容緩","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:47:38.000Z","uid":108351,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"646179a3e1be7fb6ba7290c7fcc8a262ac87c710","tid":1343066,"uid":108351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"大家以為政府諗住賴示威者引哂啲警力去港島，但係政府已經出咗新聞稿，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋係想入埋元朗打人條數入返送中度</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469604-20190722.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469604-20190722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcpa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=8579251e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469604-20190722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=37b8cf90\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469604-20190722.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n可想而知今次係佢哋有計劃地打嘅一場輿論戰。我哋嘅文宣一定要從攻守兩方面考慮：<br />\n<br />\n守：<br />\n1. 講返送中示威者同元朗白衫嘅分別。以返送中示威者嘅行為（例如71立會）同白衫（無差別襲擊）做例子。<br />\n2. 連落何君堯度（例如用下面條片）<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2150144851781577&amp;id=330920327037381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2150144851781577%26id%3D330920327037381&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcpa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=535aa2a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2150144851781577&amp;id=330920327037381</a><br />\n<br />\n攻：<br />\n1. 點解警察唔做嘢<br />\n1a. 打999，999話驚就唔好出街，之後cut線<br />\n1b. 元朗同天水圍警署落閘，置當區治安於不顧<br />\n2. 警力調配問題<br />\n2a. 不合理地置過多警力於港島，忽視其他地區治安<br />\n2b. 放大警察喺西環同元朗所用武力嘅分別：西環嘅示威者冇嘗試傷害過任何一個人，但係就被警方多次用催淚彈同開咗三十幾槍驅散；元朗白衫無差別襲擊就乜都唔做<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手諗吓仲有啲咩points<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80063be697544b1300975c9c1c2feb00b3a4a5e4","tid":1343066,"uid":272773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9609a25faa9fac963a15082408b3eb5fb663747","tid":1343066,"uid":63043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"有巴打找到條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/hwsp0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fhwsp0&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcpa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=4343bcb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/hwsp0</a><br />\n1.5個鐘前 係果撚台 見到在元朗站 出口接駁商場嗰條天橋 有一個黑衫人比一大班白衫人用 好長嘅棒狀物體 打到瞓低 加瞓低左再用棒打 加全地血！"},{"pid":"a348d05c8c9adb6447bfc47c119424202370359c","tid":1343066,"uid":221919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad6eb5dd494f10f73833e9653a51bd8596f50df","tid":1343066,"uid":108351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9609a25faa9fac963a15082408b3eb5fb663747","tid":1343066,"uid":63043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"有巴打找到條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/hwsp0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fhwsp0&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcpa4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=4343bcb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/hwsp0</a><br />\n1.5個鐘前 係果撚台 見到在元朗站 出口接駁商場嗰條天橋 有一個黑衫人比一大班白衫人用 好長嘅棒狀物體 打到瞓低 加瞓低左再用棒打 加全地血！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:42:53.000Z","msg":"thanks<br />\n不過對於白衫武力程度嘅論述應該唔需要太擔心？<br />\n我本人比較擔心條數被人入咗落返送中示威者度"},{"pid":"8263617a56c3a63628920357ad033edd43eb5239","tid":1343066,"uid":108351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:44:46.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"9442fb45cef439acbf1d6d21514594a3fa7e1faa","tid":1343066,"uid":63043,"like":0,"disl